      <title>独家：文件显示，裕信银行在收购股份前曾与德国高层官员进行交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-talked-top-german-officials-before-stake-buy-documents-show-2024-10-16/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社看到的议会文件显示，在收购德国政府所持商业银行部分股份的几个月前，裕信银行高管曾与德国总理府和财政部等德国政府高级官员进行过对话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/unicredit-talked-top-german-officials-before-stake-buy-documents-show-2024-10-16/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 07:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
